{"tid":573219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踢傷鄰居11歲女兒 雙程證婦判社會服務令","createTime":"2018-02-26T09:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:08:17.000Z","uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a999401f728ddbcc5689057fe446b4b92d49f363","tid":573219,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"持雙程證中年婦人在文錦渡邊境禁區居住，與相識廿年鄰居因爭拗業權後積怨，中年婦聲稱屢遭對方滋擾甚至在其家門前擺「狗屎陣」，去年10月她派人於門外加裝閉路電視監視對方，工程期間雙方再起爭執，中年婦踢跌對方11歲女兒。她早前認罪，今被判處80小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n被告孫運金（42歲）早前承認普通襲擊罪，其代表律師今指，被告為事件表示難過及後悔，同意不應將無辜事主牽涉在內，她為此表示悔疚，願意接受法律後果。律師又指被告住所曾被截水達半年之久，其間需外出取水作日常使用，這對被告構成滋擾及壓力，承諾日後會以理性方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時指法庭有責任保護小朋友，對案件極之憤慨，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟接受報告建議判被告接受社會服務令80小時</span>，叮囑被告珍惜機會，三思而行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180226/57876499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57876499&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=f52f4aa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57876499&h=f2640ac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180226/57876499</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc89a70a7471d73dc624170c3a6dce00a1b6215","tid":573219,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"狗屎陣係咩陣法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627fe5e7c4b153a136979a76f75c89a49571711c","tid":573219,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc89a70a7471d73dc624170c3a6dce00a1b6215","tid":573219,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"狗屎陣係咩陣法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"D垃圾大陸婆鳩噏都認真"}]}